Text: I think your core of classic rock albums look amazing!  I will seed and seed and seed some more once I get them down.  Sorry for cutting out abrubtly from time to time but my laptop overheats and shuts off on its own from time to time.  If the quality is good in this collection, I will do my best to seed at least one of the sets 24 hours a day for months on end.  Thank you for these particularly great uploads!
